{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_02_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 二人だけの秘密",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースの沖縄野外ライブ数日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days before the Sunny Peace Okinawa concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいな、さっきまでみんないたのに……\nさくら達はどこに行ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s odd. Everyone was here just a minute ago.\nWhere did Sakura and the others go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.133333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、鈴村さん\nサニピのみんなを探してるんだが見かけなかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Suzumura.\nI’m looking for the Sunny Peace girls. Have you seen them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら遙子さんのために\nみんなでラッキーアイテムを探しに行ったで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They all went to look for\nlucky items for Haruko.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ラッキーアイテムを探しに？\nなんでまたそんなことに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking for lucky items?\nWhy are they all doing that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "それより、話は聞いたで～\nサニピが沖縄で野外ライブするらしいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I heard something…\nApparently Sunny Peace will be doing an outdoor concert in Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄の滞在スケジュールはもう決まってはるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is the schedule for their stay in Okinawa settled already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ホテルと飛行機の手配は済ませたよ\nライブの準備が出来るよう余裕を持った日程にしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The hotel and flights are booked.\nI set the schedule so I’d have plenty of time for concert preparations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ほほう……ちなみに飛行機は何時の便？\n宿泊するホテルの名前は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So what time’s their flight?\nAnd what hotel are they staying at?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことを聞いてどうする気だ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you asking about that for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "それは……詳しく知っておいた方が\nうちも動きやすいと言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I know the details‚ it’s easier\nfor me to get things done…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "偶然を装って近づけると言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to get close to them and pretend it’s a coincidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……何を企んでいるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you scheming?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "いややわぁ、企んでるなんて人聞きが悪いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh please‚ “scheming” makes me sound devilish…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "その日はちょうどうちもオフやから\n休日を沖縄でのんびり過ごして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I happen to be free on that day‚\nso I thought I’d spend my free time relaxing in Okinawa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ついでにサニピのみんなに会って\n観光案内してあげよ思っただけや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I thought it’d be fun to meet up with Sunny Peace\nand be their tourist guide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うちが沖縄に行くことはここだけの秘密やで\n遙子さんには内緒にしといてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But me going to Okinawa is just between us‚ okay?\nDon’t tell Haruko.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "どうして内緒なんだ？\n別に隠す必要はないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why keep it a secret?\nThat’s not something you need to hide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a good one—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.33333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "……せやな、{user}さんには\nちゃんと話しておいた方がええな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I should tell you\nwhat’s going on‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "実はさっき遙子さんから\n沖縄にはいい思い出がないって話を聞いてん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing is‚ earlier I heard that Haruko\ndoesn’t have any good memories of Okinawa‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ライブする度に雨に降られて酷い目にあったから\n沖縄は苦手やって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "because she got rained on at every concert and had a tough time.\nNow she has a problem with Okinawa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "つらそうな顔でそんな話されたらほっとけへんやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was telling the story with such an agonized look‚ I have to do something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "うちも遙子さんを助けてあげたいんよ\nせやからサプライズで元気づけてあげよう思て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to help Haruko.\nSo I thought I’d cheer her up with a surprise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちはありがたいけど\nどうして鈴村さんがそこまでしてくれるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for caring about her.\nBut why are you going so far for her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さんにしてみれば\nサニピはライバルでもあるグループだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From your point of view‚\nSunny Peace is a rival group‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりのオフなんだから、俺達のことは気にせず\n沖縄でのんびり休暇を楽しんでもいいんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s your first holiday in a while‚ so rather than worrying about us‚\nshouldn’t you just take it easy in Okinawa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "……しゃあないな。ほな正直に言わせてもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess It can’t be helped. I’ll tell you the truth‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "……こんなん恥ずかしいから\nいっぺんしか言わへんよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…though it’s a bit embarrassing.\nSo I’m only gonna say this once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロから飛び出したトリエルを\n星見プロは温かく迎え入れてくれたやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we jumped ship from Van Productions‚\nHoshimi Productions gave us a warm welcome‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなにはもの凄く感謝しとる\nせやから少しでも恩返しがしたいんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so we’re really grateful to all the Hoshimi Productions people‚\nand I want to do something to repay the favor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "恩返しか……\n俺達のことをそんな風に思っていてくれたとはな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Repay the favor‚ huh…\nI never knew you thought of us like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。そういうことなら\nサニピのスケジュールを後でメールしておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ if that’s how it is‚\nI’ll send you Sunny Peace’s schedule later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "おおきに！　それでこそ敏腕マネージャーやわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks! That’s a talented manager!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ただし、あまり羽目は外さないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But please don’t go too far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "オフの間は鈴村さんの自由にしてくれていいが\n自分がアイドルであることは忘れないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can do what you like with their free time‚\nbut remember that you’re all idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "うちは節度と良識が服を着て歩いてるような人間やで\n何も心配あらへんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the living embodiment of moderation and common sense‚\nso don’t worry about a thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "言えば言うほど不安に感じるんだよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more you say‚ the more nervous I get…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、メール待ってるわぁ\n遙子さんにはくれぐれも内緒にしといてな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be waiting for your email.\nAnd you really mustn’t tell Haruko.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ。ここで話したことは誰にも言わない\n二人だけの秘密だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. I won’t tell anyone what we talked about.\nIt’s a secret between us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_01-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "秘密……ふふ、そうやね\n沖縄で会えるのを楽しみにしてますー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A secret… Hehe‚ so it is.\nI’m looking forward to meeting you in Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7866.666666666702,
          "startTime": 229.93333333333337
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
