      "text": "鈴村さんも口では茶化してるけど\n本心ではみんなのことを思ってくれているんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura doesn’t speak her mind directly‚\nbut deep down‚ she really does care about people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
